snippet: NBC on Monday announced the “SNL” guest host lineup for the first three shows of the fall season, including Ms. Fey, one of its biggest stars.
abstract: NBC announces guest-host lineup for Saturday Night Live's first three shows of its 39th season; Tina Fey, one of its biggest stars, is scheduled to host premiere.
lead_paragraph: NBC on Monday announced the “SNL” guest host lineup for the first three shows of the fall season, including Ms. Fey, one of its biggest stars.

headline.main: Tina Fey to Host Return of  ‘Saturday Night Live’
